.. code:: console

   $ abmagick hello <<< 'Hello world!'
   convert 'inline:data:image/x-portable-graymap;base64,UDUKMSAxMyAyNTUKSGVsbG8gd29ybGQhCg==' gray:hello

   $ cat hello
   cat: hello: No such file or directory

   $ abmagick hello <<< 'Hello world!' | sh

   $ cat hello
   Hello world!

